      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      What ingredients are in Ecolosophy and how do they work?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_WwRrAe-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_WwRrAe-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Ecolosophy uses a plant-based surfactant blend derived from coconut and corn, combined with citric acid (from citrus fruits), baking soda (sodium bicarbonate), and natural essential oils. The surfactants break down dirt and grease, citric acid dissolves mineral deposits and kills bacteria, and baking soda neutralizes odors. Essential oils provide natural antimicrobial properties backed by WHO research on plant-based disinfection. No synthetic fragrances, preservatives, quats, dyes, parabens, or sulfates.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_AzcABd-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_AzcABd-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      What makes Ecolosophy different from other non-toxic cleaners?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_AzcABd-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_AzcABd-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Ecolosophy is a plant-powered cleaning concentrate that replaces 100+ toxic plastic bottles with one reusable bottle. Unlike other cleaners, we use only natural plant-based ingredients with essential oils - no synthetic fragrances, preservatives, quats, dyes, or sulfates. We're Leaping Bunny certified cruelty-free and biodegradable, killing 99.9% of germs naturally while being safe for kids, pets, and the planet.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_DzHDkt-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_DzHDkt-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      Is Ecolosophy safe for kids and pets?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_DzHDkt-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_DzHDkt-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Yes! Our plant-based formula contains no toxic chemicals, synthetic fragrances, or harsh ingredients. It's hypoallergenic and non-toxic, making it safe to use on all surfaces around your family and pets without worry. You can clean countertops, floors, and toys knowing there are no harmful residues left behind.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_xeTe3p-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
