                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      What certifications does Ecolosophy have?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_xeTe3p-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_xeTe3p-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Ecolosophy is Leaping Bunny Certified (cruelty-free), which is the gold standard for animal welfare in personal care and cleaning products. We're also biodegradable, non-GMO, and formulated without toxic chemicals on the EPA's Safer Choice list. Our packaging is made from recyclable materials, and we're committed to transparent ingredient disclosure - every ingredient is listed on our label with no hidden "fragrance" chemicals.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_GtFmwP-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_GtFmwP-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
