      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      Is Ecolosophy EPA-registered or FDA-approved?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_GtFmwP-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_GtFmwP-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Ecolosophy is formulated as an all-purpose cleaner and is not required to be EPA-registered because we make cleaning claims, not pesticide claims. EPA registration is only required for products marketed specifically as disinfectants or sanitizers. However, our formula has been independently tested using EPA-approved safe ingredients, methods and kills 99.9% of common household germs. We comply with all FDA and EPA safety standards for household cleaning products.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
