                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_UDJa4k-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_UDJa4k-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p><a href="https://ecolosophy.com/collections/refills" title="https://ecolosophy.com/collections/refills">Ecolosophy Super Concentrate</a> costs $59.95 per 33.8 oz bottle (regularly $69.00). One bottle makes 100+ refills, which means each spray bottle refill costs less than 60 cents - far cheaper than buying individual cleaning products that cost $5-8 each. You'll save hundreds of dollars per year while reducing plastic waste.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_VaeaU7-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_VaeaU7-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
