      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      How many refills does one concentrate make?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_VaeaU7-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_VaeaU7-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>One 33.8 oz bottle makes over 100 spray bottle refills. That means one Ecolosophy bottle replaces 100+ plastic cleaning bottles, saving you money and dramatically reducing plastic waste. Just add one capful to water and you have a full bottle of powerful, non-toxic cleaner.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_K9wGV9-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_K9wGV9-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
