                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      Is Ecolosophy biodegradable?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_K9wGV9-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_K9wGV9-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Yes, Ecolosophy is 100% biodegradable. Our plant-based formula breaks down naturally without harming the environment. We're also Leaping Bunny certified cruelty-free, non-GMO, and packaged in refillable, reusable, recyclable bottles to minimize environmental impact.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_AwtdT9-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_AwtdT9-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      Is Ecolosophy really effective with 99.9% of germs?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_AwtdT9-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_AwtdT9-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Yes, Ecolosophy is effective against 99.9% of germs naturally using plant-based ingredients and essential oils. Our formula is scientifically proven to be as effective as harsh chemical cleaners, but without the toxic side effects. It's safe, effective, and backed by WHO-cited research on plant-based antimicrobial properties.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_Q3nybj-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_Q3nybj-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      Can Ecolosophy be used on all surfaces?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_Q3nybj-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_Q3nybj-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Yes! Ecolosophy is safe for virtually all surfaces including countertops, glass, stainless steel, tile, wood, laminate, painted surfaces, and appliances. It's gentle enough for food-contact surfaces (no rinsing required) and won't damage or discolor most materials. Avoid using on unsealed natural stone like marble or granite, as the citric acid can etch the surface. Always test in an inconspicuous area first if you're unsure.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_8UPenF-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_8UPenF-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      How long does one bottle last for an average household?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_8UPenF-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_8UPenF-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>For an average household, one 33.8 oz bottle of Ecolosophy Super Concentrate lasts 6-12 months with regular use. If you clean daily (kitchens, bathrooms, counters), you'll make approximately 100+ spray bottles, which equals about 8-10 months of cleaning. Light users can stretch it to a full year or longer. Compare this to buying 8-10 individual cleaning products every month - Ecolosophy saves you $300-500 per year while eliminating 100+ plastic bottles from landfills.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_xDF9pX-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_xDF9pX-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      What's the difference between Ecolosophy and other "natural" cleaners like Seventh Generation or Method?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_xDF9pX-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_xDF9pX-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Unlike many "natural" brands that still contain synthetic fragrances, preservatives, and undisclosed ingredients, Ecolosophy uses 100% plant-based ingredients with full transparency. We're a concentrate (not pre-diluted like most brands), so one bottle replaces 100+ bottles - drastically reducing plastic waste and shipping emissions. We're also more cost-effective: at less than 60 cents per refill vs. $4-6 for competitors. Plus, we're Leaping Bunny certified cruelty-free, which many "natural" brands are not.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_F3XFGi-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_F3XFGi-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      Does Ecolosophy have any harsh chemical smell?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_F3XFGi-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_F3XFGi-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>No! Ecolosophy has a light, natural scent from essential oils (Citrus Burst and Pure Serenity) or no scent at all (Unscented Oasis). Unlike conventional cleaners that use synthetic fragrances and harsh chemicals like ammonia or bleach, Ecolosophy smells fresh and clean without overpowering fumes. The scent dissipates quickly after cleaning, leaving no chemical residue or lingering odor. Safe for people with sensitivities, allergies, or asthma.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_efLLdh-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_efLLdh-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      Can I use Ecolosophy if I have allergies or chemical sensitivities?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_efLLdh-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_efLLdh-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Yes! Ecolosophy is hypoallergenic and formulated specifically for people with allergies, asthma, and chemical sensitivities. We contain no synthetic fragrances, dyes, or harsh chemicals that trigger reactions. Our <a href="https://ecolosophy.com/products/unscented-oasis-all-purpose-cleaner" title="https://ecolosophy.com/products/unscented-oasis-all-purpose-cleaner">Unscented Oasis</a> formula is completely fragrance-free for those sensitive to essential oils. Many customers with Multiple Chemical Sensitivity (MCS) use Ecolosophy as their only cleaner because it's gentle, non-toxic, and doesn't cause respiratory irritation or skin reactions.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_8gyWb8-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_8gyWb8-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      Is Ecolosophy really better for the environment than regular cleaners?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_8gyWb8-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_8gyWb8-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Yes - dramatically better. One Ecolosophy bottle replaces 100+ plastic bottles, preventing approximately 15 pounds of plastic waste from entering landfills or oceans. Our plant-based formula is 100% biodegradable and breaks down naturally without polluting waterways. We use minimal packaging, concentrated formulas reduce shipping emissions by 95%, and our bottles are refillable and recyclable. Conventional cleaners contain petroleum-based chemicals that persist in the environment for decades and harm aquatic life.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_fhkrpz-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_fhkrpz-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      Does Ecolosophy kill mold and mildew?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_fhkrpz-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_fhkrpz-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Yes, Ecolosophy is effective against mold and mildew on hard, non-porous surfaces. The combination of plant-based surfactants, citric acid, and natural essential oils (particularly in our Citrus Burst formula) disrupts mold cell membranes and prevents regrowth. For best results on visible mold, spray the affected area, let it sit for 5-10 minutes, then scrub and wipe clean. For mold prevention, clean surfaces weekly with Ecolosophy to inhibit spore growth. While not an EPA-registered mold remover, our formula is highly effective for household mold maintenance in bathrooms, kitchens, and basements.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_iYFNwq-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_iYFNwq-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      How long does Ecolosophy take to kill germs?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_iYFNwq-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_iYFNwq-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Ecolosophy kills 99.9% of common household bacteria within 30-60 seconds of contact time on hard, non-porous surfaces. For best results, spray the surface thoroughly, let it sit for at least 30 seconds (or up to 5 minutes for tougher jobs), then wipe clean. This is comparable to most conventional cleaners, which also require contact time to be effective. Unlike instant-evaporating sprays, Ecolosophy's formula stays wet long enough to break down bacteria, viruses, and mold without harsh chemicals.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_TLT3WR-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_TLT3WR-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      Is Ecolosophy as effective as Clorox or bleach?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_TLT3WR-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_TLT3WR-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Yes, for everyday cleaning and disinfection. It is effective, just like Clorox, but without toxic chlorine bleach, harsh fumes, or chemical residue.  For home use - kitchens, bathrooms, counters, floors - Ecolosophy delivers the same germ-killing power as Clorox without the health risks or environmental damage.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_LLg87X-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_LLg87X-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      Can Ecolosophy replace all my cleaning products including bleach?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_LLg87X-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_LLg87X-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Yes, for 99% of household cleaning tasks. Ecolosophy replaces all-purpose cleaners, glass cleaners, bathroom cleaners, kitchen degreasers, and daily disinfectants. It kills 99.9% of germs without bleach, ammonia, or harsh chemicals.  For most families, one bottle of Ecolosophy truly replaces 15+ conventional products, saving money and dramatically reducing plastic waste.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_HXGe3U-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_HXGe3U-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      Does Ecolosophy work on tough stains like grease and soap scum?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_HXGe3U-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_HXGe3U-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Yes! Ecolosophy's plant-based surfactants are highly effective at breaking down grease, oil, soap scum, and hard water deposits. For tough kitchen grease, spray generously, let it sit for 2-3 minutes, then wipe or scrub. For soap scum in showers and tubs, spray the surface, let it sit for 5 minutes, then scrub with a brush or sponge. The citric acid in our formula dissolves mineral buildup, while the surfactants cut through oil and grease. For extremely stubborn stains, you may need to repeat or use a stronger dilution (2 capfuls instead of 1).</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_NXmj7Y-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_NXmj7Y-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      Is Ecolosophy safe to use around food prep areas?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_NXmj7Y-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_NXmj7Y-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Absolutely! Ecolosophy is safe for food-contact surfaces like countertops, cutting boards, and dining tables. Our plant-based formula contains no toxic chemicals, and you don't need to rinse after cleaning (though you can if you prefer). Unlike bleach or ammonia-based cleaners that leave harmful residues, Ecolosophy breaks down into water and plant matter. It's perfect for cleaning kitchens where kids eat, pet food bowls, high chairs, and any surface that touches food. Safe, effective, and no chemical aftertaste or odor.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_cf9raq-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_cf9raq-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      How does Ecolosophy compare to Lysol or disinfecting wipes?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_cf9raq-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_cf9raq-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>Ecolosophy is effective with 99.9% of germs as Lysol, but without quaternary ammonium compounds (quats), synthetic fragrances, or harsh chemicals linked to respiratory issues and hormone disruption. Lysol wipes also create massive plastic waste - Americans throw away 100 million pounds of wipes per year. Ecolosophy is a reusable concentrate: one bottle replaces hundreds of single-use wipes. You get the same disinfecting power with zero plastic waste, no toxic fumes, and significant cost savings. Plus, you can use your own reusable cloths instead of disposable wipes.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div><div
                class="accordion"
                
              >
                <details
                  id="Details-collapsible_row_LmnH8h-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  
                >
                  <summary id="Summary-collapsible_row_LmnH8h-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj">
                    <svg
    class="icon icon-accordion"
    aria-hidden="true"
    focusable="false"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="20"
    height="20"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
  ><path d="M18.5 1.5H1.5L1.5 18.5H18.5V1.5ZM1.5 0.5C0.947715 0.5 0.5 0.947715 0.5 1.5V18.5C0.5 19.0523 0.947715 19.5 1.5 19.5H18.5C19.0523 19.5 19.5 19.0523 19.5 18.5V1.5C19.5 0.947715 19.0523 0.5 18.5 0.5H1.5Z" fill-rule="evenodd"/>
      <path d="M14.9975 6.09084C15.201 6.27746 15.2147 6.59375 15.0281 6.79728L8.91631 13.4627C8.82231 13.5652 8.68987 13.6239 8.55079 13.6247C8.41172 13.6256 8.27857 13.5684 8.18335 13.4671L4.99513 10.0731C4.80606 9.87179 4.81596 9.55536 5.01723 9.3663C5.21849 9.17723 5.53492 9.18713 5.72399 9.3884L8.54335 12.3897L14.291 6.12145C14.4776 5.91791 14.7939 5.90421 14.9975 6.09084Z"/></svg>
                    <h3 class="accordion__title inline-richtext h4">
                      Does Ecolosophy leave streaks on glass and mirrors?
                    </h3>
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="icon icon-caret" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708 0L5 4.293 1.354.646a.5.5 0 00-.708.708l4 4a.5.5 0 00.708 0l4-4a.5.5 0 000-.708z" fill="currentColor">
</svg>

                  </summary>
                  <div
                    class="accordion__content rte"
                    id="CollapsibleAccordion-collapsible_row_LmnH8h-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                    role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="Summary-collapsible_row_LmnH8h-template--17518276542595__productquestions_hb8Vqj"
                  >
                    <p>No! Ecolosophy is excellent for glass, mirrors, and stainless steel. The key is using the right dilution and wiping technique: spray lightly (don't oversaturate), then wipe with a clean microfiber cloth in circular motions. For best results on glass, use a dry microfiber cloth to buff after cleaning. Unlike conventional glass cleaners with ammonia, Ecolosophy won't leave chemical residue or fumes. Many customers use it as their only glass cleaner and get streak-free, crystal-clear results.</p>
                    
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
